aphy of speaking of multilingual practices and the cultural ideas associated with them.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aLanguage and culturezAfrica. 0aLanguage and languagesxVariationzAfrica. 0aLanguages in contactzAfrica. 0aLinguistic changezAfrica. 0aMultilingualismzAfrica. 4aAfrikanische Sprachen. 4aMehrsparchigkeit. 4aSprachkontakt. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aAfrican Languages.  aLanguage Contact.  aLanguage Ideology.  aLinguistic Change.  aMultilingualism.  aSociolinguistics.1 aLüpke, Friederike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStorch, Anne, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aStorch, Anne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)z978311023845708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton Backlist 2000-2015z978311074296108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LINGUISTICS 2013z978311031724408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK 2013z9783110317237oZDB-23-DSP0 cprintz978161451251640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978161451194640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781614511946423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781614511946/original  a978-3-11-023845-7  DGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics 